data.description: Welcome to this beautiful home in Somerton! Remodeled throughout the years, this three level story home offers 4 bedrooms and 1 1/2 baths. You can see the love and dedication that the owners have put in for their home based on how beautifully maintained it is. The kitchen is newly renovated creating the perfect modern touch with it's open area. New central A/C installed. Plenty of parking space and a big backyard to enjoy the good summer days. Owners did all the work for you so you don't have too. Come take a look! This home is waiting for you.
